snippet.title: Raiders of Mizburgh gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Raiders of Mizburgh is my entry for MizJam1, a gamejam where everyone uses the same art assets. 
The game is available at https://peterofferman.itch.io/raiders-of-mizburgh
